cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a novel neural network framework for comment generation and outfit matching in fashion recommendation. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper uses a convolutional neural network to extract visual features of outfits. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with recommendation systems. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes a multi-task learning framework for joint training of outfit matching and comment generation. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with fashion images and text comments.
